Generic single-database configuration.

Run Migrations:

// make changes to your model
run "flask db migrate -m "ticket_no_description" 
OR
run "python manage.py db migrate -m "ticket_no_description"

//wait for it to generate xyz_ticket_no_description.py in Migrations folder
// check on the auto generated migration script verify/edit changes as required
run "flask db upgrade" to apply changes 

run "flask db downgrade" to rollback the latest changes

